1. Install GRPC-Java

git clone -b v1.39.0 https://github.com/grpc/grpc-java

Please refer https://github.com/grpc/grpc-java/blob/master/COMPILING.md

1.1 cd grpc-java

1.2 create gradle.properties

kxie@kxie-ubuntu-20:~/grpc-java$ more gradle.properties 
skipCodegen=true
skipAndroid=true

1.3 ./gradlew build

1.4 ./gradlew publishToMavenLocal

2. Build and run the sample code in this directory

// This code is copied from grpc project in https://github.com/eugenp/tutorials.git
// https://github.com/eugenp/tutorials/tree/master/grpc
// https://www.baeldung.com/grpc-introduction

2.1 Build the code
mvn clean package -Dmaven.test.skip=true

2.2 Run GRPC server
mvn exec:java -Dexec.mainClass=com.baeldung.grpc.server.GrpcServer

2.3 Run GRPC client
mvn exec:java -Dexec.mainClass=com.baeldung.grpc.client.GrpcClient
